@startuml
title CI Pipeline – Usage and Stages (GitHub Actions)

actor "Developer" as Dev
actor "Reviewer" as Rev

package "GitHub" {
  [Repository] as Repo
  [Pull Request] as PR
  [GitHub Actions CI\n(.github/workflows/ci.yml)] as CI
}

package "CI Stages" {
  [Checkout code] as S1
  [Install deps\n(requirements.txt + requirements-dev.txt)] as S2
  [Format check\nruff format --check] as S3
  [Lint\nruff check] as S4
  [Unit tests\npytest] as S5
  [Security scan\nbandit] as S6
  [Dependency audit\npip-audit] as S7
}

Dev --> PR : open/update PR
PR --> CI : triggers workflow
CI --> S1
S1 --> S2
S2 --> S3
S3 --> S4
S4 --> S5
S5 --> S6
S6 --> S7

CI --> PR : status checks\n(pass/fail)
Rev --> PR : review + merge when green

@enduml

